Compiler Option: -edebuginfo
=============================

Add debug information

Syntax:
-edebuginfo

Description:
The `-edebuginfo` compiler inserts debugging symbols into output files, to use
with GDB-compatible debuggers.
`-edebuginfo` is automatically implied by the `-g` option.
`__FB_ERR__` can be used to determine in user source code if the `-edebugingo`
option was specified or implied on the command line.
